findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.

findings.title: _tokenTransfer function does not check burn and marketing addresses to be excluded from reward and sender address to be excluded
findings.description: The _tokenTransfer function uses the _transferStandard function without checking if burn and marketing addresses are excluded from rewards, and also does not check if the sender's address is excluded.
